Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...what, that's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...it killed my uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...they say it's posessed by the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chico, hurry and hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, my pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This.. is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir, this is where that monster shows up, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, every day at 11:40, it comes here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! The well fills up at 11:40. After that, it evaporates from the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster knows this, and drinks when the water is highest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 10:10. So, it's another hour and a half, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is "Bagi"? Is it a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. No, it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An animal.. no.. it's also a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi is.. complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She came from japan, from the same town I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the evening of my fifteenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, crusin' this strip is bollocks, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We're gettin' off at the next ramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryosuke... Don't jump ahead of yer senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids ride in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotcha, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna have some fun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a ride! Come down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's runnin' away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be fun! Let's get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up! We gotta talk, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem hangin' out with us?! Don't freak out, dang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya wanna join the party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make a good present!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry! Step on it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That, was Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, it spared me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, I found out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was everyone in the gang killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Very badly wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't stick around, and ran home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I called it home, but it was only a place to sleep, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a delinquent, I didn't go to school, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad was a crime reporter, always on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother, being a scientist, was always shut up in her lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is Ryosuke's fifteenth birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize you're still his mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean — I can't celebrate his birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryosuke! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding around with those slobs again, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cause an accident and make the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as a crime reporter, where would I stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be a laughing stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fifteen now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you stop worrying your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't {\i1}you{\i} the one to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that— Aah-cha-chah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...So, as adults, we have responsibilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom can barely come home every three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My job forces me to spend days away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At fifteen, you can't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm away too, aren't you proud?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a student, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Skipping school and goofing off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can become a decent adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I get promoted and have more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have a nice, long talk about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When that be? One year? Three years? Ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaknow, take yer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me! Your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My god, this is the thanks I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I even came home from work early, for your birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! I'm sorry I bothered you when you were so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fuck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there. In front of that empty house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I found that chick's coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that house is the chick's hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Way ta go, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryo! What's wrong? Your first time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, watch out. She could jump at us any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! Go 'round back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of her. Maybe ain't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look! Are these dog's paw prints?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn big for a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a bear's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That chick... she's got some kinda beast to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bones! There are bones here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but they look like a bird's or dog's bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Don't freak out over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there're so many of em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya think her bear ate 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop yer tremblin'! Anyway, we're gonna wait for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout if we call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real! This is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find that girl and her monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...and give 'em a {\i1}present{\i0} they ain't gonna forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... do we really have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What... Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You sayin' you don't want to get some payback..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...on that bitch who laid us up? Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if she doesn't come tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll get 'er tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what, but... something touched my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm not sure if I-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lettin' anybody quit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit there, you damn coward. Hey, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See if she's outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... By myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Are you scared, or do I have to motivate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, if she comes after me... I ain't that tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you got more balls than this guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you know, this wasn't the pussy I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that kid's the bait. When he's down we'll jump her and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me... Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, y-you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It said it was Bagi... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, it's been a while, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi's not a monster like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, I'm surprised you don't recognize your own kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only been nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine... Nine years... Nine years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know you! I swear I don't know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can remind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Don't you recognize my.. scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when we used to sleep together?..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you could forget that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bagi{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You didn't forget me, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I owned Bagi when I was just a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I was just a little kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I miss those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Ryo! A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to see your mom, and I found it near the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? C'mon, it's a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I like dogs better, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so picky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, cats are better, they need less care...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...like a perfect child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty big! It's a weird color, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Its eyes aren't like a cat's, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll call it Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Bagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it copied me! She's really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll eat anything, see? It's eating natto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly! She wants sauce on the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi's reading a picture book!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, son, that cat's not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't die! I'll make her better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling — put the cat down and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She can't die! She's got to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My beautiful Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Up! I said up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Here's your treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi! Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi just stood on her back feet! Hurry, come and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi's dancing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote that? You... you wrote your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Its expression is intelligent and its eyes are human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's also huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It could bite someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My horoscope said this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better call the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi! Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi! Please come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I would cause trouble for you, so I left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, Bagi was a lot cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm Bagi. Appearances change after nine years, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've.. matured, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, are you a cat? Or human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... know that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I know one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,..you were the only one who loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come back, Ryo! Oh, I'm so glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Please, don't be frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a girlfriend or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? N-no, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lone wolf! And why should you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alone, too. I'm not a lone wolf though. Just.. a stray cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked for my kind everywhere, for nine years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one of my kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did I come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi.. Dad found you a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, do you.. know where I was found?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember my dad mentioning he had stopped by the research lab that day..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably found you nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the lab my mother works at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it far?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You really wanna go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My kind... maybe my family... I might see them there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Getting a bit sentimental, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Research lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the SuperLife Center?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's ten kilometers down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if this sounds a bit weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...but uh, is there any place around with cats that can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...stand on two feet like humans, and write and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, I wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if you heard anything about weird talking cats or something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,about nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T THINK BACK NINE YEARS.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I can remember what happened nine years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved from the city around then, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Much quieter here, aside from that incident that first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A dreadful commotion at the lab, it was such a ruckus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There were cats, dogs, chickens, all kinds of other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone had to stay inside, it was unheard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Well, the security in the lab came out and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,killed all the escaped cats and dogs and such!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it was awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They took guns and found and shot every last one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd they kill them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this was just a rumor at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they said they weren't like normal animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY WERE MONSTERS WHO COULD TURN YOU TO STONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Electric fence... Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can jump over that and carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Augh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lasers! Infrared cameras are following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! We'll be shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Those lights are infrared beams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They've set up a net of infrared lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you set it off, the lasers shoot you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. It won't even budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a window?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang... It's sealed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That was hardened glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it time yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,10:35.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:23:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So in about another hour, Bagi will come to drink this water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No mistake! I've seen it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.12,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, can you really kill that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi's a demon, so a human could never harm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say you were once Bagi's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...If you fought with it, you'd be massacred like the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, it's too early! it's only—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong? It fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's not Bagi! It's — a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help... Everyone's been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The village... last night... attacked! Bagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,West... Twenty kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chico! To the bike, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.72,0:24:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi killed and ate my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill and eat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.02,0:24:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see... how Bagi could attack women and children...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.18,0:24:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! Bagi's not a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.89,0:24:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a confused... unwanted child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.93,0:24:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.00,0:25:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just what kind of experiment is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're alive! They're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.08,0:25:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi! Threre's a head of you here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.28,0:25:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Dang it, don't freak me out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.58,0:25:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely, they're just being kept for later experiments...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.63,0:25:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.28,0:25:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The goat's head is... controlling a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.02,0:26:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I read that once in a sci-fi book...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.08,0:26:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...it called them cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.67,0:26:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Replacing parts of one thing with parts of something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.44,0:26:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're doing experiments on that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.62,0:26:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, these mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.33,0:26:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyborg mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.65,0:26:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.17,0:26:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... I am, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.52,0:26:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you don't look like any cyborg I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.04,0:26:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Too sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.66,0:26:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.04,0:26:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely... I was also born in this laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.73,0:26:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can figure that out if we ask my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.44,0:26:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's on the staff in this lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.97,0:26:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...! Could use a few drapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.07,0:26:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make those footsteps! The guards will hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.53,0:27:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.38,0:27:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.13,0:27:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.69,0:27:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid! Dang it, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.82,0:27:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.95,0:27:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.97,0:27:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some kind of greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.39,0:27:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's damp in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.54,0:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The plants are moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.19,0:27:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Plants do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.31,0:28:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, they're rustling. I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.45,0:28:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird they're all tropical plants. Cactuses and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.15,0:28:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, some botanist once said cactuses are plants of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.11,0:28:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently they can detect people with supernatural powers, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.51,0:28:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that from my mother once, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.80,0:28:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why they're growing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.17,0:28:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe making new kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.80,0:28:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey look! These are cool, they can grab stuff—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.06,0:28:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go — that hurts! Quit it! I'm got no superpowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.23,0:28:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,BAGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.09,0:28:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo! Above!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.99,0:29:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.52,0:29:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.18,0:29:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.28,0:29:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.78,0:29:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wups! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.02,0:29:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop or we'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.74,0:29:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.42,0:29:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.01,0:30:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.30,0:30:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang! They shot the breaker! Where are the...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.45,0:30:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo! I can see. C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Something touched my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.85,0:30:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.28,0:30:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.89,0:30:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just now two unauthorized personel were at the cactus grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.07,0:30:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave two guards serious injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.07,0:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, all the entrances were closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.17,0:30:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The locker room's been raided!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.49,0:30:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.04,0:30:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitesuits are missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.73,0:30:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitesuits, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.17,0:30:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They probably put them on
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.80,0:30:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and are roaming the Center unimpeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.74,0:30:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, don't let them reach the P-4 level.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.19,0:30:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, do you think the creature
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.05,0:30:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,could have {\i1}come{\i0} from the P-4 level?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.91,0:30:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.24,0:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The animals of the P-4 level are all accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.60,0:31:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing at the Center?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.42,0:31:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You the President here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.76,0:31:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? T-T-T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to see Professor Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.86,0:31:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no Professor Ishigami here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.04,0:31:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here? Liar! She's the head researcher here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.07,0:31:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Professor left for South America yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.16,0:31:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,South America? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.14,0:31:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She was offered a position at the Cucaracha Research Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.07,0:31:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Republic of Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.77,0:31:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that? Introduce yourself, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.33,0:31:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ishigami is my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.33,0:31:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't know she was marri--..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.45,0:31:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.58,0:31:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're able to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.29,0:31:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet my mother and ask her
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.81,0:31:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened at this research center nine years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.73,0:32:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, you explain, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.26,0:32:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.93,0:32:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.85,0:32:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That time Bagi here was picked up by my father in some alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.01,0:32:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll help. Just let go of me, Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.84,0:32:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now talk, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at SuperLife, our brilliant minds conduct
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.90,0:32:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,cutting-edge research that will benefit all humanity-
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.16,0:32:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit, what is she!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.59,0:32:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-It's a gene transfer experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.01,0:32:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is...what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.37,0:32:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother, Professor Ishigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.63,0:32:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is {\i1}the{\i0} scholar of advanced genetic engineering!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.05,0:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To an idiot like you, gene transfer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.31,0:32:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,combining a life form's genes with other genes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.00,0:32:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and making new life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.67,0:32:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has gone perfectly except for, well, nine years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.93,0:33:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! In the earthquake,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.49,0:33:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,P-4 has suffered serious damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.87,0:33:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of lab animals have escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.29,0:33:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the headcount?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.90,0:33:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.21,0:33:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Call security. Call everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.34,0:33:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate the animals. Don't leave even one alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.22,0:33:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If genetically engineered life escapes the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.37,0:33:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the ecosystem will be devastated!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.39,0:33:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ensure they don't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.60,0:34:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes fourteen animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.91,0:34:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind is the last one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.75,0:34:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the artificially inseminated American mountain lions...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.69,0:34:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...the batch implanted with human genes...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.27,0:34:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it grows, it will be especially intelligent and deadly!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.86,0:34:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't supposed to live! Search more!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.32,0:34:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.01,0:34:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a monster that shouldn't alive, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.89,0:34:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case... You were better off not knowing, right, Bagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.56,0:34:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, President Sir... if you think that all I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.77,0:35:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a creature to test some idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.11,0:35:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you're wrong! I'm alive! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.48,0:35:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm your child, whether you want me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.15,0:35:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A living creature's body is made of tiny things called cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.58,0:35:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hair, eyes, tongue... every part is just a groups of cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.04,0:35:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the center of a cell is a core called nucleus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.66,0:35:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If one looks at the nucleus carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.59,0:35:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,things called chromosomes are bunched inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.09,0:35:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In any living thing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.93,0:35:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is a respective number of chromosomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.51,0:35:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at one a million times larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.81,0:35:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda disgusting, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.32,0:35:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside it is a double spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.30,0:35:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and in {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.14,0:35:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are thousands of important things called genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.33,0:35:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These genes are passed from parent to kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.14,0:35:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and from kid to grandkid,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.08,0:35:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,copying their bodies traits!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.49,0:36:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the copying, kids are born just like their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.49,0:36:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to know what genes control the traits!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.75,0:36:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if we take out one gene...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.72,0:36:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it in another creature's chromosome...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.56,0:36:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...a new life form with a new body will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.09,0:36:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, we mixed rice, pumpkin and some other genes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.72,0:36:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and made rice ten times bigger than normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.22,0:36:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,("Normal" Rice vs "Newtype" Rice)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.61,0:36:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can put human genes in animals, breed animals with human traits,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.50,0:36:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and can study the purpose of these genes!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.46,0:36:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.36,0:36:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.00,0:36:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, I'm just some mongrel with no other kin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.30,0:36:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.73,0:36:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! Whatever your reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.70,0:36:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,these experiements are cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.42,0:36:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my mother now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.05,0:36:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at the Cucaracha Research Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.62,0:36:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Republic of Monica, by invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.22,0:36:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.43,0:37:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd recommend against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.95,0:37:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand how you feel, but as a member of this center...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.97,0:37:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to put your down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.28,0:37:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We will dissect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.43,0:37:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and after we study your innards and brain, we'll freeze your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.28,0:37:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Intelligent or not, It's the proper way to deal with a lab animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.01,0:37:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.88,0:37:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to convince me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.47,0:38:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.61,0:38:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up that pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.17,0:38:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Write what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.92,0:38:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Republic of Monica, care of Cucaracha Research Lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.85,0:38:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Yohko Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.72,0:38:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have found the remaining living animal escaped from nine years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.83,0:38:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and am sending it to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.88,0:38:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son, Ryosuke, will accompany it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.77,0:38:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow the Republican government's procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.54,0:38:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There, sign your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.92,0:38:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, order your people! Get us a plane to that country!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.79,0:38:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.84,0:38:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.54,0:38:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if I didn't, we would've been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.31,0:38:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that hypnotism?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.79,0:39:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.39,0:39:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.59,0:39:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, please don't be scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.20,0:39:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask to be able to do these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.27,0:39:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to hypnotize me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.59,0:39:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.52,0:39:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my only friend in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.90,0:39:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell your mother... my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.96,0:39:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop her horrible research and cruel experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.76,0:39:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.29,0:39:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't listen, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.83,0:39:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't...intend to kill my mother, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.71,0:39:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.23,0:39:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.52,0:39:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.53,0:39:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.91,0:39:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She left me to become a lab monster, but she's still my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.35,0:39:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to her as a son...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.79,0:39:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll convince her what she's doing is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.90,0:40:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll stop the experiments, and we'll finally have a family again!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.93,0:40:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I left my inhaler in the luggage down below...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.80,0:41:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be long, it's quite cold down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.59,0:41:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.57,0:41:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't go snooping in luggage...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.63,0:41:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you let the kid inside? We had a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.43,0:41:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,BAGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.12,0:41:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.11,0:41:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.43,0:41:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.76,0:41:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.14,0:41:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi... Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.64,0:41:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryo... look o-out...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.70,0:41:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now. You're safe now...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.60,0:41:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must have shipped the lab's cactuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.46,0:41:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with the hope of killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.83,0:41:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.06,0:41:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was requested by your {\i1}sponsor{\i0} that the creature die in-route.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.21,0:41:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't interfered, the cacti would have done that job for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.89,0:42:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have bothered with First Class...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.67,0:42:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, enjoy the rest of the trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.00,0:42:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.13,0:42:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this in a movie once!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.83,0:42:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Look, it's a kilometer to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.12,0:42:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 800 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.83,0:42:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,700 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.22,0:42:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and give me that cloth! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.07,0:42:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 500 meters now!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.19,0:42:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit counting, and pass me those cacti!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.70,0:42:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab my tail! Hang on tight and don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.94,0:42:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.09,0:42:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.21,0:43:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's below us?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.86,0:43:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.89,0:43:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see a soft place to land?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.49,0:43:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a gully ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.02,0:43:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're jumping! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.24,0:43:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,BAGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.23,0:44:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo! You're finally awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.03,0:44:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.34,0:44:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.09,0:44:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound hasn't closed yet! You shouldn't move for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.48,0:44:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lick it, it will get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.64,0:44:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out... How long will you lick it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.87,0:44:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Another three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.94,0:44:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Three whole days?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.87,0:44:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fourth day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.41,0:44:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept licking it while you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.98,0:44:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.22,0:44:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At first it was amazing—the blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.64,0:44:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This forest...are we in the Republic of Monica?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.35,0:44:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but we seem to be close to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:44:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case—let's go, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.41,0:44:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.26,0:45:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Republic has armed guards—you'd soon be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.87,0:45:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.27,0:45:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying we hide in this jungle forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.72,0:45:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, c-cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.43,0:45:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get something to eat. Wait there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.50,0:45:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Ba-Ba-B-Ba-Ba-Bagi-Bagi!— BAGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.90,0:45:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GIVE US BACK OUR DINNER!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.53,0:45:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up. You'll feel a lot better
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.65,0:45:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a snake-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.04,0:45:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,With a bad joke like that, you're fine now, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.45,0:45:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with us as a pair, we can make it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.42,0:46:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the lab, persuade my mother and take her back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.72,0:46:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when I was little, we'll start over, as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.46,0:46:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When she meets you I'm sure she'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.95,0:46:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And what'll happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.64,0:46:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me behind in this counry?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.20,0:46:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! You'll live with us! Like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.72,0:46:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll care for me, like a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.08,0:46:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! As a sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.44,0:46:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.24,0:46:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a condition. Trim your claws, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.00,0:46:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get sentimental, it gets kinda painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.17,0:46:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything! I'll trim my whiskers if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.09,0:46:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I want to show you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.34,0:46:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.01,0:46:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it from dead birds while you slept!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.17,0:46:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it look {\i1}good{\i0} on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.02,0:46:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, sure it does. You look like a fashion model.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.87,0:46:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'll try and dance for you, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.89,0:47:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Those're the aerobics you saw on TV as a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.85,0:47:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah Ryo! It's a gift for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.63,0:47:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, a squall!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.77,0:47:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's enough! You're soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.85,0:47:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.05,0:48:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out! That's my shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.12,0:48:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm washing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.56,0:48:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tail destroys windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.46,0:48:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It also cleans whites.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.46,0:48:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec—I hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.42,0:48:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a car, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.80,0:48:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, friggin' animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.30,0:48:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.81,0:49:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It worked.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.87,0:49:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bagi's hypnosis, eh?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.85,0:49:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared of me, she said, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.71,0:49:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She scares me a lot now and then!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.30,0:49:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.43,0:49:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You in the truck, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.58,0:49:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.34,0:49:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.30,0:49:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.82,0:49:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.55,0:49:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We know there are rebel guerrillas hiding around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.06,0:49:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have reason to believe you are a part of those rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.77,0:49:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll investigate. Show me proof you're with the circus!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.32,0:49:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This American lion performs tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.49,0:49:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.12,0:49:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tricks, you say? Fine, let's see it do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.46,0:50:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyrotechnics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.20,0:50:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.38,0:50:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A flaming coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.29,0:50:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass through it, and I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.77,0:50:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's impossible, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.40,0:50:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are thirty meters of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.80,0:50:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump in, and she'll be burned to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.32,0:50:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.54,0:50:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't, I'll have you executed as guerrillas!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.16,0:50:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.66,0:50:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.13,0:50:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it! She made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.96,0:50:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.59,0:51:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.60,0:51:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, son...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.67,0:51:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.42,0:51:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake, I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.02,0:51:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this is the Cucaracha Research Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.03,0:51:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.81,0:51:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, we made it. Our goal at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.80,0:51:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream. You were shipped here,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.80,0:51:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I heard that "Ishigami" was written on your shirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.47,0:51:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I jumped with surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.39,0:51:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where's Bagi— Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't move yet. Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.22,0:51:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Bagi go? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.04,0:51:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi? Oh, the lab animal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.07,0:51:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for delivering it. We'll soon dissect the specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.79,0:51:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.26,0:51:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahg, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.36,0:51:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do that?! She's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.69,0:51:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill her, why I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.61,0:51:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.68,0:51:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a research subject to further our knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.30,0:51:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't fit in anywhere on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.75,0:51:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We must dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.00,0:51:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens to Bagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.64,0:52:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you're my mother, I {\i1}will kill you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.37,0:52:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? My little Ryo—! You've changed, haven't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.29,0:52:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.24,0:52:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.09,0:52:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this stupid research right now, and lets return to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.35,0:52:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be a family, like we were before! Dad and I miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.48,0:52:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be done. I was contracted by this country's government to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.97,0:52:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, our current research will be an important breakthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.98,0:52:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in helping humanity's poorest! I can't just abandon that!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.94,0:52:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.00,0:52:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of anything besides your GOD DAMNED RESEARCH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.76,0:52:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.40,0:52:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you study hard, maybe you'll see why I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.25,0:53:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror, mirror, on the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.81,0:53:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Reveal your cats to me, and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.00,0:53:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tranquilizer darts are a bitch, hey, Bagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.02,0:53:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure you don't exert yourself, we've glued you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.41,0:53:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor will your "hypnosis" affect me through the TV screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.19,0:53:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely understand what I'm saying, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.44,0:53:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never had a subject retain intelligence after such extreme stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.00,0:53:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it seems you're quite the clever girl
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.37,0:53:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold out as long as you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.04,0:53:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have your heart frozen and take it back to Japan as a present for my colleage!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.83,0:53:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can still speak, do so. Your brain is...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.99,0:53:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say I'm sorry, that you lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.59,0:53:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...I didn't mean for you to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.71,0:53:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... do this... research...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.98,0:53:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,please... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.86,0:54:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What! You don't know how many lives we've saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.25,0:54:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands! Millions!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.45,0:54:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep going, I can save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.10,0:54:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your selfishness is disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.72,0:54:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm {\i1}not your Mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.88,0:54:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the research!.. How could it stop?...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.00,0:54:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency, we are honored to have you come
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.41,0:54:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,all this way to visit this Cucaracha Research Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.85,0:54:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ishigami, arrived from Japan with a noble cause, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.04,0:54:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The new kinds of large servings you developed...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.25,0:54:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to the starving people of our country...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.61,0:55:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,shall be a great salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.15,0:55:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.69,0:55:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the new servings we just gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.28,0:55:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.13,0:55:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems almost like bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.09,0:55:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't tested them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.51,0:55:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case, please allow us to feed them to animals before you try them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.49,0:55:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean they're not safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.39,0:55:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellency, everything made by gene transfer is a new species.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.04,0:55:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we must find out exactly what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.48,0:55:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I heard in Japan it was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.63,0:55:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... But since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.03,0:55:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we have improved the gene arrangement a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.05,0:55:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The government has been fighting rebel guerrillas for ten years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.78,0:55:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we feed these servings to the starving public,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.98,0:55:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,our reputation will improve!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.72,0:55:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! The animals that ate the rice—
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.09,0:55:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.06,0:55:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.42,0:56:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The rice we just made contained a very strong poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.06,0:56:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A poison?! No... There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.09,0:56:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, back to your room, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.49,0:56:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Semmen Bond. Your babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.72,0:56:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.66,0:56:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit still for an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.58,0:56:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you won't be shot up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.04,0:56:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.12,0:56:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour's when this critter Bagi's dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.01,0:56:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit tight 'til then.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.42,0:56:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi... is going to be killed, in an hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.06,0:56:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, back in your room, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.33,0:56:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.88,0:56:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.09,0:56:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saving Bagi no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.76,0:56:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop me if you can! Shoot if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.91,0:57:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save Bagi even if I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.86,0:57:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.44,0:57:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Put away that speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.87,0:57:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, kid, wanna test your luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.40,0:57:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet on this coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.98,0:57:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Win and I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.65,0:57:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose and, it's a pity, but I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.81,0:57:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads or tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.72,0:57:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.15,0:57:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heads. Kid, you lucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.43,0:57:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.29,0:57:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.31,0:57:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're helpless. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.08,0:57:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.90,0:57:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Below here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.90,0:57:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ishigami, it's nothing to mourn about!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.86,0:57:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.07,0:57:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.98,0:58:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In trying to make God's blessing, I've made food for the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.19,0:58:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't continue... this research anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.02,0:58:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have this horrible food disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.99,0:58:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, you don't need to throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.79,0:58:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it's useful as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.28,0:58:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellency, it is rice that contains a strong poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.98,0:58:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who eats it will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.75,0:58:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone will die? Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.71,0:58:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we feed this rice to the guerrilla rebels who oppose our government...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.05,0:58:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be wiped out where they stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.59,0:58:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.39,0:58:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.76,0:58:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We feed it to the writers who voice discontent with the government and clean them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.57,0:58:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.73,0:58:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's feed it to the scum in neighboring countries that support the guerrillas!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.39,0:58:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sweep them all away! Let's wipe them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.10,0:58:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, what a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.07,0:58:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our nation is secured... We can be of a world power!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.01,0:58:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency intends to use it to kill...?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.58,0:58:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.50,0:58:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a splendid weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.79,0:59:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Professor Ishigami, please start mass-producing this rice at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.26,0:59:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I must refuse to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.53,0:59:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Refuse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.84,0:59:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have researched to create new foods
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.00,0:59:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to help those suffering with hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.60,0:59:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot create poisonous life for murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.39,0:59:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to oppose me? You mean to defy my orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.13,0:59:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh— This is the first time I ever heard such a reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.73,0:59:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To defy me is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.53,0:59:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the rice like I told you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.79,0:59:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a scientist. I cannot assist in murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.82,0:59:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.82,0:59:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning, you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.62,0:59:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you try setting foot outside this lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.06,0:59:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those attack dogs will tear your body to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.35,0:59:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.84,0:59:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.46,0:59:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on... Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.52,1:00:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're glued down! The bastards...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.90,1:00:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it... It's no good. If I pull you off, your fur will tear.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.55,1:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bond, tell me how to free her.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.03,1:00:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop acting spoiled. Give it up and go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.48,1:00:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm a good boy, so tell me!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.58,1:00:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.02,1:00:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to tell me?! Then let's fight! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.38,1:00:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't piss me off for real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.07,1:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, let's bet with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.37,1:00:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Win and I'll tell you. Lose and go to your room. Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.01,1:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tails!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.83,1:00:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain. You won.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.12,1:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is the glue. This is the glue remover.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.08,1:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, we have no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.90,1:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,R-R-Ryo... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.91,1:01:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, okay. Bagi, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.06,1:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.45,1:01:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryo... I c-can't stand, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.33,1:01:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't talk w...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.51,1:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you don't need to stand. We'll still run away.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.23,1:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.77,1:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to run away? Playtime's over now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.72,1:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.06,1:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.82,1:01:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an idiot would come this far and not run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.48,1:01:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just humored you. Was it fun for you, kid?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.85,1:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang... You were making fun of us?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.12,1:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a sucker to catch on now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.87,1:01:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You be careful I don't use this. Go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.16,1:01:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.90,1:01:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Bagi! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.43,1:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find us some wheels! You look for my mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.98,1:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.06,1:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,An elevator!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.75,1:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo. Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.27,1:02:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Crap! It's going up!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.28,1:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.06,1:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.04,1:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.19,1:02:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's Kikuchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.01,1:02:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is that... That...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.72,1:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother—I mean, Professor Ishigami is on what floor?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.93,1:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What have I been doing all this time?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.43,1:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed I could make anything with the power of science.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.64,1:02:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in the end, I made something this horrible.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.26,1:02:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't go back from here...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.35,1:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ishigami, it's the President's order.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.05,1:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking the rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.38,1:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take things over from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.68,1:03:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand that over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.62,1:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting it. Tell that to the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.99,1:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you defy his orders, you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.19,1:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.13,1:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.03,1:03:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring out my mother, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.25,1:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you just in case, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.55,1:03:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bite my mother, or claw her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.33,1:03:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet at the main entrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.71,1:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.74,1:03:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo... please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.30,1:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once... please stroke... my throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.32,1:03:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.82,1:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.36,1:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be killed soon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.45,1:03:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But before that, I must take this plastic-hardened{\b1} poisonous rice away from here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.07,1:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this rice is ever cultivated, it'll be too late.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.34,1:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no knowing how many billions will die.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.33,1:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're here. The attack dogs, no doubt.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.65,1:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bagi!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.20,1:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.36,1:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.39,1:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.67,1:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.84,1:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in luck! There are bikes here. Two of them, even!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.99,1:04:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Planning to escape?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.43,1:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.06,1:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.04,1:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you this blade's rust.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.48,1:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away?! You coward!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.06,1:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cool it, you war freak!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.39,1:05:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.70,1:05:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.03,1:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.03,1:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.81,1:05:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, over here! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.58,1:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.68,1:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.00,1:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been bitten to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.30,1:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi is...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.04,1:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.09,1:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.68,1:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.09,1:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.85,1:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Bagi bite you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.44,1:06:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it... When she promised that much!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.20,1:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... Heck if I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.20,1:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.61,1:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You bit Mom to death and ran off, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.88,1:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You really pulled a big one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.80,1:07:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid... You show some promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.43,1:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come after me?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.69,1:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, no. I got fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.00,1:07:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I let you get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.35,1:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.03,1:07:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.67,1:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My, aren't we pissed off?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.95,1:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi got my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.23,1:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That dang cat... She hated my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.13,1:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She bit her to death and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.60,1:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. It's like being bitten by your pet dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.17,1:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi's not a pet dog! She's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.94,1:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I trusted her, but she...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.71,1:07:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead ain't comin' back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.81,1:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.00,1:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find Bagi and kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.74,1:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get her back for betraying me!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.93,1:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting revenge?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.06,1:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll beat her dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.39,1:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it, kid?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.45,1:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bond, I'm asking you. Teach me how to use a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.08,1:07:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach you how to use a gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.89,1:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... If I'm as good as you, I can kill Bagi, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.76,1:07:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For how much?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.19,1:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.13,1:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No chance in heck.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.97,1:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.56,1:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I get Bagi, I'm not returning to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.18,1:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind a girl cryin' on my arm, but you...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.69,1:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck... Lose, and give it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.80,1:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads or tails.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.45,1:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tails.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.27,1:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, heck, I'm dang unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.08,1:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.27,1:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We eat first. Don't worry, I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.51,1:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years later
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.74,1:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.65,1:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.77,1:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I sit there?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.80,1:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other places to sit, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.56,1:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sit in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.94,1:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot and stuffy. No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.56,1:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the government—
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.97,1:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishigami, Ryo... We are from the government public safety department.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.78,1:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.23,1:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, indeed, you have ruined a large laboratory of ours...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.89,1:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing great damage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.90,1:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's been five years since then. Situations have changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.83,1:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come to ask a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.05,1:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you are a free-willed gunman.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.50,1:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to take care of a certain creature.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.29,1:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That creature's name is—
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.69,1:09:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That creature's name is Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.84,1:09:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this kinda critter.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.18,1:09:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.82,1:09:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately... It's been attacking villages here and there,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.50,1:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and has bitten dozens of people to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.12,1:09:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now, many hunters have gone after Bagi,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.04,1:09:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but all wound up half dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.04,1:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can beat that monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.82,1:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill Bagi, we'll pay you ten thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.01,1:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.09,1:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, for you to be able to return to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.72,1:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll include a passport, visa, and all the other documents!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.02,1:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what would you say? Since Bagi was once your pet,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.76,1:10:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to say you can't kill it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.37,1:10:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.33,1:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like the deal's off. Adios, señor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.82,1:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it. Do you know where this Bagi is?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.93,1:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a kid who knows. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.90,1:10:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To find out from him, we need to borrow your skill.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.94,1:10:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way in heck!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.01,1:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where Bagi is. But I'm not telling anyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.06,1:10:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem, Chico.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.70,1:10:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way! I'm never telling!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.06,1:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi killed my dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.62,1:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to get Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.09,1:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.25,1:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your conditions?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.00,1:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How about splitting the reward?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.98,1:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.58,1:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! What a skill!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.86,1:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take me on and win, I'll show you where Bagi is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.10,1:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.03,1:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.86,1:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If my rock hits, it'll crush your nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.41,1:11:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yah, bravo, bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.03,1:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost, sir. It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.44,1:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.83,1:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be useful. Prepare me a motorcycle, and a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.67,1:12:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad was walking down the street when Bagi bit him to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.07,1:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've thrown a rock and killed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.79,1:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sight. The village's wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.44,1:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's horrible. Too horrible!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.86,1:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi's a demon, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.86,1:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.12,1:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong. These prints don't seem to be of one creature.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.83,1:12:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there are two or three, at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.90,1:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, there couldn't be two or three Bagis.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.80,1:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even little babies are bitten to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.05,1:13:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor things.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.06,1:13:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chico, careful!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.25,1:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right? Your wound?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.77,1:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.96,1:14:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.90,1:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a normal American lion.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.51,1:14:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there were four of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.27,1:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones attacking the villages weren't Bagi.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.71,1:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is...!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.86,1:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is the string of dad's bolas!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.31,1:14:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned it from my dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.72,1:14:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad fought this one and got bitten to death!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.05,1:14:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.21,1:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my dad's!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.86,1:14:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, maybe... It may be a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.62,1:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster attacking people and villages, and Bagi...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.59,1:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,are different!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.82,1:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are military helicopters.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.22,1:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.03,1:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'd say they're following us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.73,1:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would they follow us?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.01,1:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally figuring out what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.00,1:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A dirty trick, you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.56,1:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Señor Ryo Ishigami, thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.74,1:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is over. Could you let us take over from here?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.31,1:15:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.30,1:16:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You suckered me into thinking I'd fight the monster and used me as a guide,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.43,1:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so you could hunt it down with your army.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.00,1:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pay you the reward, as promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.77,1:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no problems then, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.28,1:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish off Bagi on our own. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.76,1:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This was arranged from the beginning, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.66,1:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That kid wouldn't show us where Bagi was.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.52,1:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we used you and had the kid show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.63,1:16:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it happens we followed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.69,1:16:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi didn't turn out to be a man-eater!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.08,1:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If that critter eats people or not, I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.60,1:16:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's with this overblown chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.05,1:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi ran off with a rice ball that's a deadly poisonous weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.45,1:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to retrieve the rice ball and report to the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.02,1:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, my soldier friends, go and attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.79,1:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Draw out the creature!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.86,1:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is it gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.91,1:17:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? C'mon and answer me!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.91,1:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it there or not?!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.54,1:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The traitors!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.05,1:18:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-An attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.29,1:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.00,1:19:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You dared to kill my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.03,1:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.85,1:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.07,1:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! C'mon and fight, Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.89,1:19:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't, I'll make you come!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.07,1:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.01,1:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Something's shining on Bagi's chest! She's wearing something!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.51,1:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.53,1:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.45,1:19:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.76,1:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.01,1:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.60,1:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.04,1:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.10,1:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.90,1:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The bike! The bike! She's aiming for it!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.30,1:20:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, the last blow?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.17,1:20:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Indians encircle the cavalry and tighten the ring,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.17,1:20:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and attack at once.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.43,1:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It means you can kill me in any way you want now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.40,1:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my end. But you're dying with me, Bagi!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.03,1:21:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir... You did it! You did it, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.05,1:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were done for!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.86,1:21:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so too, but Bagi hesitated...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.54,1:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...from killing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.51,1:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it. This was shining really bright.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.88,1:21:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see. This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.06,1:21:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the pendant my mother wore.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.32,1:21:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.90,1:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's last words.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.31,1:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am having Bagi escape with a rice ball.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.08,1:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have instructed her to bury the rice ball in a mountain, hiding it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.02,1:21:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of her intelligence has vanished,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.57,1:21:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but she must have understood my request.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.12,1:22:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should he know I betrayed him,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.24,1:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the President no doubt will have me killed by attack dogs.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.01,1:22:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bagi will return to the wild.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.55,1:22:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probably, she will end her life in the mountains.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.23,1:22:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life forms like Bagi and the rice ball should not be made by humans.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.57,1:22:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have been a bad scientist, and a bad mother.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.55,1:22:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryosuke, I'm sorry. Take care... Bagi too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.52,1:22:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.47,1:22:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi didn't kill my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.44,1:22:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother let her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.01,1:22:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so? Why did you keep it to yourself, Bagi?!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.97,1:22:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had said anything, I would've taken you back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.59,1:22:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have become family and we'd have lived together like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.53,1:22:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi... Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.56,1:22:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Japan together!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.01,1:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't die, Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.07,1:23:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.44,1:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.25,1:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi we brought here, and left out back,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.09,1:23:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared this morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.25,1:23:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.32,1:23:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we left her here, and covered her up, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.11,1:23:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See, she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.79,1:23:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody took away the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.39,1:23:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... What are those?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.95,1:23:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Paw prints!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.18,1:23:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Bagi's paw prints!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.97,1:23:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I mean, Bagi died for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.27,1:23:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she came back!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.08,1:23:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The prints disappear past that thicket.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.73,1:23:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi was alive... and she went to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.64,1:23:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's what happened, Chico!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.65,1:23:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she went back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.70,1:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter. Bagi, live through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.29,1:24:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagi, live all you can. I'm praying for it!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.01,1:24:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't show up in front of humans again, probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.05,1:24:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.65,1:24:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation: Owen Henderson, Machiko Yanagawa
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.06,1:24:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Trans. Materials: Noel Tominack & Machiko Yanagawa
